            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Hd1e108">Rubrica 18</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De iudiciali misericordia: venia et impunitate</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>¶ De iudiciali misericordia: 
               ve<lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>nia: et impunitate. Rubrica. 18
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e118">SAlustius in iugurtino:</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e127">Ignoscendo
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>malis bonos perditum itur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e132">Tullius rethor artis vereris li. i.
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e137">His qui imprudentes leserut ignosci conuenit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e144">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e146">Ouidius de ponto lib. i. e. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e148">Multa nietu
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>cohibet qui pena pauca cohercet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e154">
               <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e158">Iacobus apostolus epistola vnica</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e158">Iudicium sine 
               mi<lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>sericordia illi qui non facit misericordiam: super
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>exaltat autem misericordia iudicio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e166">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e172">Seneca de clementia:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e170">Uenia est pene 
               meri<lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>te remissio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e176"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e182">Idem de moribus:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e178">Bonis 
               no<lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>cet qui malis parcit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e184">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e194">Lex diges. ti. ad le. iulis magist. l. famofi. §. i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e188">Lubricum lingue ad penam facile trahendum non
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e196"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e205">Titu. de penis. l. absentem.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e198">Sacius
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>est impunitum reliqui facinus nocentis quam 
               inno<lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>centem damnare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e207"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e218">Ti. de bonis eorum qui ante 
               sen<lb ed="#V" n="89" break="no"/>tentiam etcaetera. l. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e209">Ignoscendum est his qui 
               sangui<lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>nem suum qualitercumque redemptum voluerunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e217">
               <lb ed="#V" n="91"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e233">Auctor libri de for. honeste vite. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e221">Erro <!--146.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="60-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1" break="no"/>ri facile veniam dato.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e251">Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 2. e. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e237">Benigni 
               prin<lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>cipis est ad clementie commodum transilire 
               ter<lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>minos equitatis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e245"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e263">Lib. 3 e. 47.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e247">Nisi culparum
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>occasiones emergerent locum pietas non 
               habe<lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>ret. Casibus asperis prestandum est sub 
               iu<lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>stitie laude moderamine: vt nec vindictam
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>finamus superare peccata: nec culpam 
               insulta<lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>re patiamur legibus impunitam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e261"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e281">Libro. 4.
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>e. 29.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e263">Non habet venie locum qui deliquit 
               ad<lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>monitus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e271"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e294">Li. 11. et pe e. 41. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e273">Ocium tibi
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>clemens actus inducit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e280">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e307">Gregorius in pastorali. cap. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e284">
               Discipli<lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>na vel misericordia multum destituitur: si vna 
               fi<lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>ne altera teneatur: sed erga subditos suos 
               in<lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>esse rectoribus debet: et iuste consulens 
               mise<lb ed="#V" n="17" break="no"/>ricordia et pie seuiens disciplina. 
               Misericor<lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>dia est lenitas cum seueritate: faciendo 
               quod<lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>dam ex vtroque temperamentum: vt neque 
               mul<lb ed="#V" n="20" break="no"/>ta asperitate exulcerentur subditi: neque nimia
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>benignitate soluantur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e305"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e332">22. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e307">Cum non 
               ma<lb ed="#V" n="22" break="no"/>litia sed sola ignorantia vel <sic>insirmitate</sic> delin <!--"infirmitate" with 's'-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>quitur: profecto necesse est vt magno 
               modera<lb ed="#V" n="24" break="no"/>mine ipsa delicti correctio temperetur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e317"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e350">41. c</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e319">Nonunquam mansueti cum praesunt vicinum et quasi 
               iu<lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>xta positum torporem defidie patiuntur: et 
               plerum<lb ed="#V" n="27" break="no"/>que nimia resolutione lenitatis vltraquam 
               neces<lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>se est vigorem districtionis emoliunt.</quote>
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>     
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e333">
               <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e369">Isidorus in sinonima soliloquiorum. li. 2. c. 49.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e337">Impia iustitia est humane fragilitati non 
               igno<lb ed="#V" n="32" break="no"/>scere. Non ames damnare: sed emendare potius
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>et corrigere. Tene rigorem in discussone 
               iusti<lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>tie: misericordiam in diffinitione sententiae.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e349"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e384">50. c</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e351">In ambiguis dei iudicio reserua sententiam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e357">
               <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e395">Mattheus vindocinensis in poetria: parte
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>2. et fi. c. 13. et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e361">Transgressionis impunitas
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>magistra est transgressionis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-d1e370">
               <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Rd1e411">Montenarius in luna cleri. c. 72.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d45220-Qd1e374">Omnis 
               fre<lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>quentari: facit impunitio crimen.
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Accendit culpam: facilis dimissio pene.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
